extendedInfo.description: The THINK Conference was created by CO-OP Financial Services to put a fresh perspective on the challenges and opportunities faced by credit unions every day. It's a credit union event for credit union employees, but you won't find the standard conference format or see typical industry speakers. What you will find is innovation and inspiration, leaving you with actionable, take-home insights to help your credit union succeed.The THINK 13 mobile app provides quick access to conference details including agendas, speaker and venue information, and social media feeds. Users will also be able to submit their vote for the THINK Prize 13 grand prize winner of $10,000Keywords: CO-OP, THINK, CO-OP Financial Services, THINK Conference, THINK 13
